data_mangement

Class RedBlackBST<Key extends java.lang.Comparable<Key>,Value>

  • java.lang.Object
    • data_mangement.RedBlackBST<Key,Value>

  • public class RedBlackBST<Key extends java.lang.Comparable<Key>,Value>
extends java.lang.Object
    the red black bst is used to store all the zip codes. this makes it easy to prevent hash misses as we can get any keys in a range easily from the redblack-bst, and because we hash objects using these keys it makes them accessible.
